\f1\b0 \cf0 The application includes the following files for Docker support:\
\pard\tx360\pardeftab720\li360\fi-360\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \'95	
\f2 .dockerignore
\f1 \
\'95	
\f2 Dockerfile
